		{"id":"1d50caa5171ce9cd","type":"text","text":"# Action System\nResponsible for communicating game actions to other gameplay systems\n- `Perform(action)`\n\t- Queues up an action to process\n- `AddReaction(action)`\n\t- Reacts to an in-progress Game Action","x":-696,"y":-623,"width":398,"height":285,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"a53b6e058d37f151","type":"text","text":"# Game State\nHolds all data related to the current game state. The game state should be accessible from any/all gameplay systems.","x":-1160,"y":-116,"width":340,"height":180,"color":"#4354d0"}
